6 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Disk Encryption',NULL),(12,12,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Email Encryption',NULL),(13,13,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-31 14:54:12','Chat Encryption',''),(14,14,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-11-01 03:32:07','Web Browsers','**Warning for mobile devices &amp; Tor:** Websites using HTML5 &lt;video&gt; tags will leak &lt;video&gt;-related DNS queries and data transfer outside of Tor.'),(15,15,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-31 14:53:02','Web Anonymity',''),(16,16,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Cryptocurrencies',NULL),(17,17,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Disk Encryption',NULL),(18,18,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Email Encryption',NULL),(19,19,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-31 14:53:47','Chat Encryption',''),(20,20,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-11-11 03:24:28','Email Accounts','Switch from a proprietary service like Gmail to one of the more transparently-run email providers below.\r\n\r\nFor more email providers, take a look at [Privacy-Conscious Email Services](http://prxbx.com/email/). Please decide for yourself whether if you trust them with your data. For more discussion about safe email providers, please see [issue #461](https://github.com/nylira/prism-break/issues/461). '),(21,21,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-31 14:56:47','Web Search',''),(22,22,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-31 14:57:33','Media Publishing',''),(23,23,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-31 14:56:17','Cloud Storage',''),(24,24,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-31 14:56:11','Chat Accounts',''),(25,25,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-24 13:59:11','World Maps',NULL),(26,26,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-24 13:59:20','DNS Services',NULL),(27,27,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-11-03 04:17:03','Operating Systems','The only way to have full control over your personal data is to run your own server. This is not for everyone though, as it requires considerable time investment and technical knowledge.'),(28,28,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Analytics',NULL),(29,29,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Anonymous Networks',NULL),(30,30,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Cloud Storage Server',NULL),(31,31,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','DNS Server',NULL),(32,32,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Email Server',NULL),(33,33,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Hardware & Software Setup',NULL),(34,34,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Publishing Server',NULL),(35,35,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','SIP Server',NULL),(36,36,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Social Network Server',NULL),(37,37,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','Tor Relay',NULL),(38,38,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','VPN Server',NULL),(39,39,'en','2013-10-06 13:11:51','2013-10-06 13:11:51','XMPP Server',NULL),(40,5,'de','2013-10-06 13:12:43','2013-10-06 13:12:43','Betriebssysteme',NULL),(41,5,'ar','2013-10-06 13:36:57','2013-10-06 13:36:57','نظام تشغيل',NULL),(42,6,'ar','2013-10-06 13:37:59','2013-10-06 13:37:59','نظام تشغيل',NULL),(43,27,'ar','2013-10-06 13:38:06','2013-10-06 13:38:06','نظام تشغيل',NULL),(44,40,'en','2013-10-25 09:58:49','2013-11-02 12:00:43','Operating Systems (Live)','A live distribution is the fastest and easiest way to a secure operating system. All you have to do is create a bootable CD or USB drive with the files provided and you\'re set. Everything else will be configured for you.'),(45,41,'en','2013-10-29 04:15:39','2013-10-31 13:05:32','App Store','Google Apps for Android are proprietary apps that come with most Android devices. After flashing your firmware with either Cyanogenmod or Replicant, protect your data by not re-installing them.\r\n\r\nIf you cannot flash your firmware, consider uninstalling Gapps with [this guide](https://cidofficial.neocities.org/010.html) by ciddaemon.'),(46,42,'en','2013-10-31 15:11:28','2013-10-31 15:11:28','Web Browser Addons',''),(47,43,'en','2013-11-01 06:15:25','2013-11-06 03:29:51','Web Browser Addons','If you\'re using a browser based on Mozilla Firefox, you can safeguard your browsing habits and stop advertising companies from tracking you by installing the following addons.'),(48,44,'en','2013-11-06 11:19:18','2013-11-06 11:19:18','World Maps',NULL),(49,45,'en','2013-11-06 11:22:00','2013-11-06 11:22:00','World Maps',NULL),(50,46,'en','2013-11-06 11:32:40','2013-11-08 02:35:08','VPN Services',''),(51,47,'en','2013-11-06 11:36:45','2013-11-06 11:36:45','Web Hosting',NULL),(52,48,'en','2013-11-08 02:20:43','2013-11-08 02:20:43','Online Office Suite',NULL),(53,49,'en','2013-11-08 02:27:20','2013-11-11 02:52:44','Email Alternative','Consider replacing email entirely with one of the following projects.'),(54,50,'en','2013-11-10 06:46:34','2013-11-11 02:50:43','Email Clients','This section contains free email clients that support PGP encryption either by default or with a plugin.'),(55,51,'en','2013-11-11 13:11:27','2013-11-11 13:11:27','Email Clients',NULL);
